Package org.achartengine.model

Provides the classes that handle the data values (data model) to be used by displaying the charts.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CategorySeries A series for the category charts like the bar and pie ones.
MultipleCategorySeries A series for the multiple category charts like the doughnut.
RangeCategorySeries A series for the range category charts like the range bar.
TimeSeries A series for the date / time charts.
XYMultipleSeriesDataset A series that includes 0 to many XYSeries.
XYSeries An XY series encapsulates values for XY charts like line, time, area, scatter... charts.
XYValueSeries An extension of the XY series which adds a third dimension.
 

Package org.achartengine.model Description

Provides the classes that handle the data values (data model) to be used by displaying the charts.
